line_1: And form the whole with fairest symmetry.
line_2: Sees lights and shades unite in due degree,
Might nothing meet the wistful eye,

line_1: Without regard to use or symmetry:
line_2: Tales upon tales they raise ten stories high,

line_1: In nice disorder and wild symmetry,
In nice disorder and wild symmetry,
line_2: Emboss'd, and pillars huge of costly porphyry.
